metadata.name: Entangled Reality
metadata.description:
**Entangled Reality**, 2022 

Original Edition, 1 of 1
Generative vector art
MP4, 3840x2160

A contemplative journey into the unseen world around us.  

Using a minimal amount of colors and a precise juxtaposition of shapes and harmonic motion, each piece challenges the intricate ways in which the human eye perceives.  

The collection is inspired by the ephemeral and intangible moments of life: unspoken words & feelings that can't be encapsulated in a singular understanding.
